               <provenance>Several individuals are mentioned in the
                     supplication formulas, written in a secondary hand: e.g., ʾabuna Gabra Qirqos (e.g., 3ra, 12vb), Walatta Bǝrhān (e.g., 3ra), ʾAmata Māryām (e.g., 3va, 7vc),
                     Gabra Māryām (e.g., 3vb, 7rb, 9vc), Zarʾa Masqal
                     (e.g., 4rc, 7vb), Habta Śǝllāse (e.g., 5rb, 9ra), Tasfā Śǝllāse (e.g., 5rb). The same individuals are also mentioned in Additio
                     1.</provenance></history>
